    ARM: mx51: Fix the address space length for SSI
    
    On MX51 the address space length for SSI is 16KB.
    
    Signed-off-by: Fabio Estevam <fabio.estevam@freescale.com>
    Signed-off-by: Sascha Hauer <s.hauer@pengutronix.de>

